{"tid":2080994,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"神父甘浩望辦集會爭港人內地子女居港權　斥政府帶頭加劇中港矛盾　憂國安法通過後無法發聲","createTime":"2020-06-27T00:47:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T02:01:48.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f9f78f6b0992b562d8e2e7d8e2c22cb37ec0876e","tid":2080994,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T00:47:18.000Z","msg":"積極為港人內地子女爭取居港權的神父甘浩望，曾於 1 月 8 日在政總外絕食 8 日，抗議政府在 1999 年向人大提請釋法，令部分港人無法與在內地居住的子女家庭團聚。甘浩望表示，政府早前以疫情原因拒絕一早答應的會議，他不滿政府拖延進度，擔心港區國安法通過後再沒有機會發聲。今日（ 26 日）甘浩望聯同 8 名爭取子女居港權人士，先後到入境事務處及政府總部遞請願信，並於晚上在遮打花園舉行集會，要求政府盡快回應訴求，否則會再度絕食。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%94%98%E6%B5%A9%E6%9C%9B%E8%BE%A6%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%E7%88%AD%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%B3%E5%B1%85%E6%B8%AF%E6%AC%8A-%E6%96%A5%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%B8%B6%E9%A0%AD%E5%8A%A0%E5%8A%87%E4%B8%AD%E6%B8%AF%E7%9F%9B%E7%9B%BE-%E6%86%82%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E5%BE%8C%E7%84%A1%E6%B3%95%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2594%2598%25E6%25B5%25A9%25E6%259C%259B%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%2588%25AD%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25AC%258A-%25E6%2596%25A5%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%258A%2587%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259F%259B%25E7%259B%25BE-%25E6%2586%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2580%259A%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%25B3%2595%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%2581%25B2%2F&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2h%2FUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=f782633b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2594%2598%25E6%25B5%25A9%25E6%259C%259B%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%2588%25AD%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C